{"tid":583640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過係街同啲死癈中開拖","createTime":"2018-03-07T07:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T08:10:21.000Z","uid":161743,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6662aebc2e0fba7305dafbec2773e553a9d888","tid":583640,"uid":161743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"今朝去茶餐廳食早餐<br />\n同2條死癈中(夫妻嚟 約48到54歲左右) 搭枱<br />\n佢老母 佢大動作郁張枱 整撚到我個沙嗲牛麵啲汁出哂嚟 仲冇撚嘢咁款 <br />\n我睥9佢  條死癈中仲要寸柒柒咁問我睥乜9<br />\n我即刻開佢拖 對佢對鬧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友食飯仲要抬隻腳上嚟食紋哂身 佢呢啲又樣柒又身為社會低下層嘅癈中真可悲 望佢2個聽日出街比車撞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為民除害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2996fc1c189b7bb0ab88f44d6ff3f0ff72dd5d62","tid":583640,"uid":98961,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:33:17.000Z","msg":"Ff完啦，抹乾淨佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18af2837c1a54acaaee3d871676ff5aa63895df","tid":583640,"uid":894,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"睥鳩人地就當開咗拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b615f1c3d216107ec346f88fb41ecfaee2c6d40a","tid":583640,"uid":168414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:39:16.000Z","msg":"就係唔夠膽開拖先上黎開po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44abe2f840ddcab26c562164f41a4262f5895f3d","tid":583640,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"213729c8e73451a9a9c8b840e264a66c3cd79012","tid":583640,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44abe2f840ddcab26c562164f41a4262f5895f3d","tid":583640,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}